                     <interp inst="t18470920-2253-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> stealing 6 spoons, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the property of <persName id="t18470920-name-1281" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18470920-name-1281" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470920-name-1281" type="surname" value="JENKINS"></interp>
